rows.label: qst701710_msg0001
rows.name:
I hoped you'd be quaking in your boots
but you're as calm as can be, ain'tcha.
You really are a merciless killer.

rows.label: qst701710_msg0002
rows.name: Think what you like.

rows.label: qst701710_msg0003
rows.name:
I've just been waiting for this day to
come for a long time. I'm ready to
face it.

rows.label: qst701710_msg0004
rows.name:
Tell me you did it. I want to hear
you say you killed her.

rows.label: qst701710_msg0005
rows.name:
As good as. If it wasn't for my reckless
ambitions, she'd still be here.

rows.label: qst701710_msg0006
rows.name:
Why did I think we'd be able to
be together? It was unbearably na√Øve
in retrospect.

rows.label: qst701710_msg0007
rows.name:
She...she used to talk about how there
was someone she wanted to support...
Someone with a dream of a better life...

rows.label: qst701710_msg0008
rows.name: It's all ancient history now.

rows.label: qst701710_msg0009
rows.name:
Just get it over with. I won't stop you.
I deserve it. Everyone else who was
involved is dead and gone. Just me left.

rows.label: qst701710_msg0010
rows.name:
Kill me now. Put an end to it. You'll get
your revenge, and maybe God
will accept my attempts at atonement.

rows.label: qst701710_msg0011
rows.name: Prepare yourself!

rows.label: qst701710_msg0012
rows.name: Stop!

rows.label: qst701710_msg0013
rows.name: Who will you help?

rows.label: qst701710_msg0014
rows.name: Jelyco

rows.label: qst701710_msg0015
rows.name: Dio

rows.label: qst701710_msg0101
rows.name:
Jelyco-san's a good person. Let's see
where this goes for a bit?

rows.label: qst701710_msg0102
rows.name:
Atonement, he says. Is that why you've
been giving people help without
accepting anything in return?

rows.label: qst701710_msg0103
rows.name: I'm not pretending I think it's enough.

rows.label: qst701710_msg0104
rows.name:
And you think dyin' would be?
You really think that's what my
sister woulda wanted?

rows.label: qst701710_msg0105
rows.name:
Strewth, mate, you don't wanna die
to make amends. You wanna die so
you can stop feeling so guilty!

rows.label: qst701710_msg0107
rows.name:
I don't give a rat's fart whether you
live or die, but pissing on what she
woulda wanted...I can't forgive that.

rows.label: qst701710_msg0108
rows.name:
When you stop feeling sorry for
yourself, come find me and we'll
discuss our strategy.

rows.label: qst701710_msg0109
rows.name: Strategy? For what?

rows.label: qst701710_msg0110
rows.name:
For wiping the Bloody Lobsters out
once and for all, mate! You and me!
This thing won't be done until we do.

rows.label: qst701710_msg0111
qst701710_msg0112
rows.name:
You're off your rocker.
You're... Wait, you're serious?

rows.label: qst701710_msg0113
rows.name:
...I can't believe it.
You really are your sister's brother...

rows.label: qst701710_msg0114
rows.name: Has brawly-fight ceased?

rows.label: qst701710_msg0115
rows.name:
Morumo very worried, so came as
fast as possible. What happen?

rows.label: qst701710_msg0116
rows.name: Er, it's kind of a lot to explain.

rows.label: qst701710_msg0117
rows.name:
I'm sorry if we caused any concern.
Everything seems to be in order now.

rows.label: qst701710_msg0118
rows.name:
Changing the past, eh?
Easier said than done. In the end, I
wonder if we're all just victims of fate.

rows.label: qst701710_msg0119
rows.name: Tell me, Minochi..

rows.label: qst701710_msg0120
rows.name:
Does that serene outlook have
anything to do with your transformation
into a Man-Eater?

rows.label: qst701710_msg0121
rows.name:
Not like you to be so direct.
Thinking of giving it a go yourself?

rows.label: qst701710_msg0122
rows.name:
I'm merely interested. As one Blade to
another.

rows.label: qst701710_msg0123
rows.name:
Well, drop it. You don't wanna end up
like me - a lousy mongrel.

rows.label: qst701710_msg0124
rows.name: Is that truly how you feel?

rows.label: qst701710_msg0125
rows.name:
You can't claim to speak for everyone.
At least, it must be different when one
goes into it of one's own accord...

rows.label: qst701710_msg0126
rows.name: What are you saying?

rows.label: qst701710_msg0127
rows.name:
If you think of yourself as a mongrel,
that's how people will see you. You
should try looking on the bright side.

rows.label: qst701710_msg0128
rows.name: Always with that positivity, Adel.

rows.label: qst701710_msg0129
rows.name:
If you want things to go well, you
have to visualize it first!

rows.label: qst701710_msg0130
rows.name:
Give me strength...
I swear being around you lot is going
to drive me round the bend.

rows.label: qst701710_msg0201
rows.name: We have to stop Jelyco-san!

rows.label: qst701710_msg0202
rows.name:
Don't even think about getting in my
way! I've waited too long for this!
